title: alex arbuckle
content: I'm a software developer who lives in Kansas City, Missouri. I have a Bachelor of Science degree in **Computer Science**. I've previously done contract work for a group of venture capitalists where I built **algorithms**, **visualization** and **interactivity** components for large sets of data. I have had the honor of participating in university class group projects, as well as various distinctive **independent projects**, including the development of this website.

As a developer, I consider myself a life-long learner, so I enjoy learning more about software development and deployment every opportunity I get. I'm a fan of both object-oriented and functional paradigms and I enjoy combining the skills I learn into projects that I display on my GitHub. *You can find more about them in the segment, **my projects**!*
